{"tid":2340361,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"linear algebra 高手入","createTime":"2020-12-25T11:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T12:22:25.000Z","uid":385670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c036360f460504090d7d473b3df4ef435867008","tid":2340361,"uid":385670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:29:51.000Z","msg":"關於vector space 同column space<br />\n假設前者係 all 2D real vectors 組合而成嘅一個空間(R2）, 咁x-y plane上面每一處都屬於佢嘅vector space;<br />\n<br />\n而column space, 喺x-y plane上面假設有個2x2 嘅matrix, 將呢兩條vector 頭尾無限延伸(span) , 再任意將佢哋乘某個數再相加兩條column = linear combination = 理論上所有組合可以reach 到x-y plane 上面嘅每一點<br />\n<br />\n所以我想問以下兩個statement 啱唔啱:<br />\n1. 喺一個R2嘅vector space入面, 如果兩條vector都係linearly independent, 咁呢個情況係咪vector space = column space ? 因為呢兩條columns 嘅linear combinations 係可以reach 到任何一點<br />\n2. 承上, 如果呢兩條vector 喺同一條線上, let's say (1,2) and (-1,-2), 咁呢個情況佢哋嘅column space 就係一條線?"},{"pid":"c74fa183a78cfb484868e569f8a988cf738b1471","tid":2340361,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4acc13acee1d293e6e821b51b29cff58fb0e65d1","tid":2340361,"uid":366141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"1. 我覺得係<br />\n2. 我都覺得係<br />\n<br />\n樓主數學唔差，繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：dse數學有5，接近全港最高分，樓主有咩問題可以再問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fc23e49994d6db2171ca33ef8679c62c01610c","tid":2340361,"uid":385670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c74fa183a78cfb484868e569f8a988cf738b1471","tid":2340361,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e2a368e7bb3ed88594ad67dc3d25a592488494","tid":2340361,"uid":385670,"like":0,"dis